Another thing you could look at... your lifter ,, or cam lobe may be in 
trouble.. you can pull a lifter and look at the cam lobe very easily. 

If you have a sunken valve,, the valve clearance tightens up.. if you have a 
flat cam lobe,, the clearance gets bigger... 

